txt.en: Wanted: Shattered Hatchets from West Rohan. Collect them to earn a reward suitable for a collector in Derndingle.

Ents of Fangorn Forest Task: Shattered Hatchets
The Ents of Fangorn Forest have a task to collect trophies from defeating their enemies in the Westemnet. These can be turned in for a reward.
